    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior is clean with only minor rock chips and light surface scratches consistent with careful use, while the interior remains in great shape with no tears or heavy stains. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a consistent service history, making it a reliable choice for its next owner. You can expect a solid, dependable car that shows pride of ownership without the premium price of a mint-condition show car.",
