      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this fantastic find! This vehicle has been well-loved and consistently maintained, making it a reliable and stylish choice for its next owner. While it shows some light signs of careful use, it remains in great shape both inside and out, offering a smooth drive and many more miles of enjoyment. It's a solid, honest car that's ready for your next adventure!",
