    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle offers a perfect balance of luxury and performance for the discerning driver. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear bumper tell the story of enjoyable highway miles. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort; the premium upholstery is supple and free of tears, and all electronic features\u2014from the intuitive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014function exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is solid, having recently undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection and full synthetic oil service. The engine delivers smooth, responsive power, while the transmission shifts seamlessly through every gear. It sits on a set of high-quality all-season tires with significant tread life remaining. Included with the sale are two sets of keys, the original owner's manual, and a detailed folder of service records, providing peace of mind that this car has been treated with respect. It is ready for its next chapter and represents an excellent value for someone seeking a reliable, premium driving experience.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
